{"tid":1803629,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅色教育成幼兒園必修課　童遭洗腦仇視外國欲拿槍打「日本佬」","createTime":"2019-12-30T10:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T12:43:07.000Z","uid":279854,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8a0573ead4457f417331e653ce405769751ea5","tid":1803629,"uid":279854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/chinas-patriotic-education-schooling-or-indoctrination/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fchinas-patriotic-education-schooling-or-indoctrination%2F&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=3dadf428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/chinas-patriotic-education-schooling-or-indoctrination/</a><br />\n為了培養忠心順服的共產主義建設者和接班人，中共正推廣「紅色愛國主義」活動，要求幼兒園的孩子懷著崇敬的心情重溫中國的革命歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>幼兒宣誓效忠共產黨</strong><br />\n「無論我生在何處，我身上始終流淌著祖國的血液，生不能改，死不能變，為了這一切，我用我的生命承諾，我用我的榮耀宣誓，我愛我的祖國！」9月25日，江西省永修縣一所幼兒園舉行了隆重的升旗儀式，老師帶著懵懂的孩子們在國旗下宣誓效忠中共及國家領導人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U87xX8H31k0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU87xX8H31k0&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=d74e7906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U87xX8H31k0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>愛國必修課</strong><br />\n「一顆紅心向太陽，一顆紅心向著黨」，10月底，江西一所幼兒園的孩子們穿著紅軍、八路軍的服裝，喊著口號參加「軍民大生產」活動。家長則被要求身穿軍裝、工農服裝耕地、插秧、施肥，重現當年「軍民大生產」的情景。「軍民大生產」是抗日戰爭時期（1937－1945年）共產黨在其控制區域內發動的一場軍隊屯田、鼓勵生產的群眾運動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7KVqoid-WY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7KVqoid-WY&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=965b48b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7KVqoid-WY</a><br />\n<br />\n但不是每個人都贊成這種教育方式。有家長告訴《寒冬》，中共「極端的愛國主義教育是世界上最邪惡的洗腦」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共斥資數十億散佈謠言<br />\n您願捐出幾美元挽救真相嗎？</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/donate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fdonate%2F&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=e71c136d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/donate/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《寒冬》因為資金不足的問題已經停左翻譯德法日3種語言</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e64e859bace3d125a7aef2e2c7950029a3b8658","tid":1803629,"uid":305536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:47:18.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=3494056a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=88bed395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要34000人 </span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803447</a></span><br />\n<sp